high_descs: Turn around and go to the toilet
Grab the spray bottle off of the toilet
Back up and look down at the trash can
Put the bottle in the trash can
Go straight to the toilet
Grab the spray bottle off of the toilet
Back up and look down at the trash can
Put the bottle in the trash can

high_descs: Turn around and then to the right to face the toilet.
Pick the bottle up from the left side of the back of the toilet.
Back up and face the trash can on the left of the toilet.
Put the bottle in the trash can.
Look up to face the back of the toilet.
Pick the bottle up from the back of the toilet.
Move to the left to face the trash can to the left of the toilet.
Put the bottle in the trash can.

high_descs: Face the opposite direction and go to the far wall, then turn right to face the toilet and go near the toilet.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle on the left from the back of the toilet.
Turn all the way around to the left one time.
Put the spray bottle into the green bin to the left of the toilet.
Go closer to the toilet.
Pick up the remaining yellow spray bottle.
Turn to look behind you, then face the toilet again.
Put the spray bottle in the bin to the left of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles to a bathroom waste bin.
